<br>
Don't compare the two, to do so is idiotic.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/utarskxev.showPublicProfile?language=EN>TarskXev</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The Original Deity</span><br>  Posts: 1026<br> <font color=#330000>(9/2/02 7:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=329.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why?</span><hr size=1> No, the rant about Maiden's Eye loot whores is about people spamming the zone (and the people fighting there in tells) looking for loot that they're not high enough level to honestly earn yet, and it's about those same lower-level players causing trains and death to the people who are appropriate to hunt there.<br>
<br>
I understand your concerns about not being left with enough mobs to kill, and god knows I don't step on any lower-level toes. Last week I was running through Paludal and got aggro from one of the bandits there. Did I kill it? No, although I would've been justified in doing so. I led it over to where a Mage was soloing shrooms and I let her kill it, whilst I chain-taunted, so it didn't even hit her pet once.<br>
